123
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:08,000
 unless you were trying to avoid people.

124
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:13,000
 And we're going to discover this woman had a lot of relational baggage.

125
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:15,000
 She had a past. She had a present.

126
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:18,000
 She had some real shame that she carried.

127
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:21,000
 In other words, Samaritans were outcasts.

128
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:25,000
 She was an outcast of outcasts.

129
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:28,000
 She's going to the well at noon to avoid people.

130
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:34,000
 And she shows up, and her worst case scenario that she can imagine is sitting at the well.

131
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:36,000
