144
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:29,000
 you would have asked him, and he would have given you living water.

145
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:31,000
 So imagine, you're this lady. You're sitting at the well.

146
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:33,000
 There's this stranger that's sitting there.

147
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:35,000
 I mean, to us, we read that, and we see the imagery.

148
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:37,000
 We know it's an illustration. It's beautiful.

149
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:40,000
 You would ask me, it would give you living water.

