177
00:14:10,000 --> 00:14:13,000
 What you have said is quite true."

178
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:20,000
 And now we begin to understand why this woman was showing up in the middle of the hottest part of the day

179
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:23,000
